{"tid":2049147,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共回應英方：專制？香港師承英國殖民式獨裁 英方自中回力鏢令人發笑","createTime":"2020-06-03T09:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T09:11:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"216a5647e4daef60c260c003fdf4437f88d1c6e0","tid":2049147,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"中方就英外相回應港區國安法提出嚴正交涉<br />\n03.06.2020 16:46<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文到國會就香港問題發表聲明，指英方不反對香港自行為國家安全法立法，但強烈反對中國強行為香港立法，認為一旦實施港區國安法，將會違反基本法，令一國兩制終結，英方將聯同國際夥伴進一步回應。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅說，中方不滿及反對英方粗暴干涉香港事務及中國內政，已向英方提出嚴正交涉。趙立堅說，英國同香港的歷史聯繫，源於侵略殖民和不平等條約，英國還妄稱香港國家安全立法是「專制」立法，所謂「專制」一詞正是英國曾經對香港進行殖民統治的真實寫照，奉勸英方認清及尊重香港已經回歸，是中國一個特別行政區的事實，否則必將<span style=\"color: gold;\">搬起石頭砸自己的腳</span>。(<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪詞窮啦? )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298457&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1298457%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BIgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=b4de87c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298457&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"565da565d3aed3afc5e39fb2eebf1fab4891d3f1","tid":2049147,"uid":283912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"又砸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b